<STAGE><HI>Enter</HI> Leopold.</STAGE>
<P>I &s;ay, Peter, Ghita's coming this way. Now don't you &s;ay any thing to her, becau&s;e you won't keep your|&s;elf
<PB N="28" REF="28">
cool; leave me to manage her, I know no more about the&s;e matters than you do.</P>
