<STAGE><HI>Enter</HI> Lilla.</STAGE>
<SP>
<SPEAKER><HI>Leop.</HI></SPEAKER>
<P>Lilla, my dear, come here, I want to &s;peak with you&mdash;now you know that I never put my&s;elf into a pa&s;&s;ion&mdash;but a lie provokes me, therefore have a care; now I expect you to tell me the truth, for Ghita has con|fe&s;s'd the whole matter.</P>
