</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER><HI>Peter</HI></SPEAKER>
<P><STAGE><HI>A&s;ide to</HI> Leopold.</STAGE>Now Leopold, I tell you&mdash;</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER><HI>Leop.</HI></SPEAKER>
