</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER><HI>Leop.</HI></SPEAKER>
<P>I know&mdash;here's a pretty piece of bu&s;ine&s;s,</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER><HI>Lilla.</HI></SPEAKER>
<P>Well, if you won't tell me, Ghita will,<STAGE><HI>To</HI> Ghita,</STAGE></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER><HI>Leop.</HI></SPEAKER>
