<L>By the lov'd hand of the favourite Fair,</L>
<L>Toils forgetting, plea&s;ure courting,</L>
<L>Beauty beaming, &s;miles tran&s;porting,</L>
<L>Bright the laurel of victory gracing</L>
<L>The manly, &amp;c.</L>
